Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
* "Pound for Pound", the best office in Hawthorn
* One of the best inner suburban locations
* Flexible areas
* Tremendous bang for your rental buck!
* Fitted and ready to go
* Take part or take it all!

600 Glenferrie Road offers excellent, corporate head office accommodation in the heart of Hawthorn.  Large, efficient floor plates enjoy excellent natural light to all sides, complimented by a light well!  

The offices are flexible in size and can accommodate areas from 200 to 3,718* sqm.

Basement car parking for staff and on site visitors spaces make this one of metro Melbourne's best office opportunities.  

Walk to all of the retail amenity and offering of the Glenferrie Road shopping strip. For lunch, pick from Taco Bell, Boost Juice, McDonalds, Sushi Hub, Sushi Sushi, Huxtaburger, Roccoco and Fonda), with plenty of health and fitness offerings in the immediate area (think Jetts, Orange Theory, F45 and Anytime Fitness).

After work, there is an excellent plethora of bars and restaurants for celebrations, after work drinks and socialising (when we can).  This brilliant location is only a short stroll to the Glenferrie train station and with the tram stop almost at the front door, getting in to the office for your staff is a dream, they'll thank you for it.  Four stops and you're into the CBD.

Please feel free to contact the listed agents as an opportunity like this will not last long.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: CLOSE TO EVERYTHING! COST EFFECTIVE OFFICE SPACE WITH SOMETHING FOR EVERYONE...
